<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A lalna gam nusien,
 Van Lal cha a hung pieng;
 Bethlehem bawng In ah,
 Gankuong sunga sam bang
 Zalin nau bang A kap,
 Khuo ei tuoh manin maw,
 Albang in A vai ie.

[V2]
 2. Khuo ei tuoh manin maw,
 Van Lal cha A hung Pieng;
 Lu ngakna nei loin.
 I hinna dingun aw.
 Gimtheih tincheng A thuok,
 Tha A kie tai, Lalpa,
 Kalvari tang chung ah.

[V3]
 3. Aw, Kalvari tang khu,
 Ka en chim thei puoh ie;
 Ka Lal thakiekna mun,
 Tuolthatte bangin maw,
 Kraws chungah a khai ui.
 Tibanga thi hi mi,
 A um um hung endiu.

[V4]
 4. Midang chu a thih tieng,
 Sau lun sunga zalin;
 Zatam in a gal ui,
 Ka Lal thakie chu vang,
 Kalvari tang chunga,
 Mipin a taihsan ui,
 Gilote kal A ngak.</lyrics>
<title>Van Lal Cha!</title>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>74</hymn_number>
</song>